安装

java jdk

To check your Java version, run the following command:
java -version
On systems with Java installed, this command produces output similar to the following:

java version "1.7.0_45"
Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build 1.7.0_45-b18)
Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (build 24.45-b08, mixed mode)

如果没有安装的话参考：http://openjdk.java.net/install/index.html

logstash 

1. wget https://download.elastic.co/logstash/logstash/logstash-1.5.5.tar.gz
   tar xzvf logstash-1.5.5.tar.gz
   cd logstash 
   bin/logstash -f *.conf
2. yum install logstash  或者sudo apt-get install logstash
   参考：https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/logstash/current/package-repositories.html